 "cells": [

   "id": "31758e0f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#  Plane stress quad model visualization"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "9c9902c6",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "This model code  from [Plot stress distribution of a plane stress quad model](https://opsvis.readthedocs.io/en/latest/ex_quads_4x4.html)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "659e9a02",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import opstool\n",
    "import openseespy.opensees as ops\n",
    "import opstool.vis.pyvista as opsvis"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d8ddc2d9",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Model"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "a894e58b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ops.wipe()\n",
    "ops.model(\"basic\", \"-ndm\", 2, \"-ndf\", 2)\n",
    "ops.node(1, 0.0, 0.0)\n",
    "ops.node(2, 0.0, 1.0)\n",
    "ops.node(3, 0.0, 2.0)\n",
    "ops.node(4, 0.0, 3.0)\n",
    "ops.node(5, 0.0, 4.0)\n",
    "ops.node(6, 1.0, 0.0)\n",
    "ops.node(7, 1.0, 1.0)\n",
    "ops.node(8, 1.0, 2.0)\n",
    "ops.node(9, 1.0, 3.0)\n",
    "ops.node(10, 1.0, 4.0)\n",
    "ops.node(11, 2.0, 0.0)\n",
    "ops.node(12, 2.0, 1.0)\n",
    "ops.node(13, 2.0, 2.0)\n",
    "ops.node(14, 2.0, 3.0)\n",
    "ops.node(15, 2.0, 4.0)\n",
    "ops.node(16, 3.0, 0.0)\n",
    "ops.node(17, 3.0, 1.0)\n",
    "ops.node(18, 3.0, 2.0)\n",
    "ops.node(19, 3.0, 3.0)\n",
    "ops.node(20, 3.0, 4.0)\n",
    "ops.node(21, 4.0, 0.0)\n",
    "ops.node(22, 4.0, 1.0)\n",
    "ops.node(23, 4.0, 2.0)\n",
    "ops.node(24, 4.0, 3.0)\n",
    "ops.node(25, 4.0, 4.0)\n",
    "\n",
    "ops.nDMaterial(\"ElasticIsotropic\", 1, 1000, 0.3)\n",
    "\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 1, 1, 6, 7, 2, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 2, 2, 7, 8, 3, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 3, 3, 8, 9, 4, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 4, 4, 9, 10, 5, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 5, 6, 11, 12, 7, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 6, 7, 12, 13, 8, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 7, 8, 13, 14, 9, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 8, 9, 14, 15, 10, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 9, 11, 16, 17, 12, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 10, 12, 17, 18, 13, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 11, 13, 18, 19, 14, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 12, 14, 19, 20, 15, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 13, 16, 21, 22, 17, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 14, 17, 22, 23, 18, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 15, 18, 23, 24, 19, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "ops.element(\"quad\", 16, 19, 24, 25, 20, 1, \"PlaneStress\", 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "ops.fix(1, 1, 1)\n",
    "ops.fix(6, 1, 1)\n",
    "ops.fix(11, 1, 1)\n",
    "ops.fix(16, 1, 1)\n",
    "ops.fix(21, 1, 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "ops.equalDOF(2, 22, 1, 2)\n",
    "ops.equalDOF(3, 23, 1, 2)\n",
    "ops.equalDOF(4, 24, 1, 2)\n",
    "ops.equalDOF(5, 25, 1, 2)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "9799508d",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ops.timeSeries(\"Linear\", 1)\n",
    "ops.pattern(\"Plain\", 1, 1)\n",
    "ops.load(15, 0.0, -1.0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "0af1c966",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/jpeg": "",
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=1024x768>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "on_notebook = True\n",
    "jupyter_backend = \"static\"\n",
    "# on_notebook = False\n",
    "# jupyter_backend = None\n",
    "\n",
    "opsvis.set_plot_props(point_size=0, notebook=on_notebook)\n",
    "fig = opsvis.plot_model(show_nodal_loads=True, show_ele_loads=True, show_outline=True)\n",
    "fig.show(jupyter_backend=jupyter_backend)\n",
    "# fig.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a0ea4e8e",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Results visualization"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "0ce1aaeb",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ops.constraints(\"Transformation\")\n",
    "ops.numberer(\"RCM\")\n",
    "ops.system(\"BandGeneral\")\n",
    "ops.test(\"NormDispIncr\", 1.0e-8, 6, 2)\n",
    "ops.algorithm(\"Linear\")\n",
    "ops.integrator(\"LoadControl\", 0.1)\n",
    "ops.analysis(\"Static\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "cebfb3ee",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "<pre style=\"white-space:pre;overflow-x:auto;line-height:normal;font-family:Menlo,'DejaVu Sans Mono',consolas,'Courier New',monospace\"><span style=\"color: #cf6275; text-decoration-color: #cf6275; font-weight: bold\">OPSTOOL</span> <span style=\"color: #12e193; text-decoration-color: #12e193; font-weight: bold\">::</span>  All responses data with _odb_tag = <span style=\"color: #008080; text-decoration-color: #008080; font-weight: bold\">1</span> saved in \n",
       "<span style=\"color: #ff4f81; text-decoration-color: #ff4f81; font-weight: bold\">g:\\opstool\\docs\\src\\vis\\pyvista\\.opstool.output/RespStepData-</span><span style=\"color: #ff4f81; text-decoration-color: #ff4f81; font-weight: bold\">1.</span><span style=\"color: #ff4f81; text-decoration-color: #ff4f81; font-weight: bold\">nc</span>!\n",
       "</pre>\n"
      ],
      "text/plain": [
       "\u001b[1;38;2;207;98;117mOPSTOOL\u001b[0m \u001b[1;38;2;18;225;147m::\u001b[0m  All responses data with _odb_tag = \u001b[1;36m1\u001b[0m saved in \n",
       "\u001b[1;38;2;255;79;129mg:\\opstool\\docs\\src\\vis\\pyvista\\.opstool.output/RespStepData-\u001b[0m\u001b[1;38;2;255;79;129m1.\u001b[0m\u001b[1;38;2;255;79;129mnc\u001b[0m!\n"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "ODB = opstool.post.CreateODB(\n",
    "    odb_tag=1,\n",
    "    compute_mechanical_measures=True,  # compute stress measures, strain measures, etc.\n",
    "    project_gauss_to_nodes=\"copy\",  # project gauss point responses to nodes, optional [\"copy\", \"average\", \"extrapolate\"]\n",
    ")\n",
    "for _ in range(10):\n",
    "    ops.analyze(1)\n",
    "    ODB.fetch_response_step()\n",
    "ODB.save_response()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "id": "119111f3",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "<pre style=\"white-space:pre;overflow-x:auto;line-height:normal;font-family:Menlo,'DejaVu Sans Mono',consolas,'Courier New',monospace\"><span style=\"color: #cf6275; text-decoration-color: #cf6275; font-weight: bold\">OPSTOOL</span> <span style=\"color: #12e193; text-decoration-color: #12e193; font-weight: bold\">::</span>  Loading response data from <span style=\"color: #34bf49; text-decoration-color: #34bf49; font-weight: bold\">g:\\opstool\\docs\\src\\vis\\pyvista\\.opstool.output/RespStepData-</span><span style=\"color: #34bf49; text-decoration-color: #34bf49; font-weight: bold\">1.</span><span style=\"color: #34bf49; text-decoration-color: #34bf49; font-weight: bold\">nc</span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">...</span>\n",
       "</pre>\n"
      ],
      "text/plain": [
       "\u001b[1;38;2;207;98;117mOPSTOOL\u001b[0m \u001b[1;38;2;18;225;147m::\u001b[0m  Loading response data from \u001b[1;38;2;52;191;73mg:\\opstool\\docs\\src\\vis\\pyvista\\.opstool.output/RespStepData-\u001b[0m\u001b[1;38;2;52;191;73m1.\u001b[0m\u001b[1;38;2;52;191;73mnc\u001b[0m \u001b[33m...\u001b[0m\n"

      ]

     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fig = opsvis.plot_unstruct_responses(\n",
    "    odb_tag=1,\n",
    "    slides=False,\n",
    "    step=\"absMax\",\n",
    "    ele_type=\"Plane\",\n",
    "    resp_type=\"StressesAtNodes\",  # or \"stressesAtGauss\", \"strainsAtNodes\", project_gauss_to_nodes needs to be set prior\n",
    "    resp_dof=\"sigma_vm\",\n",
    "    show_defo=True,\n",
    "    defo_scale=\"auto\",\n",
    "    show_model=True,\n",
    ")\n",
    "fig.show(jupyter_backend=jupyter_backend)"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "927dccff",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Interacting with Pyvista"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "1c5bab71",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Since version 1.0.18, opstool provides a function ``get_unstruct_responses_dataset`` that returns a pyvista [UnstructuredGrid](https://docs.pyvista.org/api/core/_autosummary/pyvista.unstructuredgrid#pyvista.UnstructuredGrid) so that you can take advantage of all the functionality on it."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "0339bf6e",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pyvista as pv"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "id": "1b450bf8",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "<pre style=\"white-space:pre;overflow-x:auto;line-height:normal;font-family:Menlo,'DejaVu Sans Mono',consolas,'Courier New',monospace\"><span style=\"color: #cf6275; text-decoration-color: #cf6275; font-weight: bold\">OPSTOOL</span> <span style=\"color: #12e193; text-decoration-color: #12e193; font-weight: bold\">::</span>  Loading response data from <span style=\"color: #2dde98; text-decoration-color: #2dde98; font-weight: bold\">g:\\opstool\\docs\\src\\vis\\pyvista\\.opstool.output/RespStepData-</span><span style=\"color: #2dde98; text-decoration-color: #2dde98; font-weight: bold\">1.</span><span style=\"color: #2dde98; text-decoration-color: #2dde98; font-weight: bold\">nc</span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">...</span>\n",
       "</pre>\n"
      ],
      "text/plain": [
       "\u001b[1;38;2;207;98;117mOPSTOOL\u001b[0m \u001b[1;38;2;18;225;147m::\u001b[0m  Loading response data from \u001b[1;38;2;45;222;152mg:\\opstool\\docs\\src\\vis\\pyvista\\.opstool.output/RespStepData-\u001b[0m\u001b[1;38;2;45;222;152m1.\u001b[0m\u001b[1;38;2;45;222;152mnc\u001b[0m \u001b[33m...\u001b[0m\n"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    },
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "UnstructuredGrid (0x2147cd223e0)\n",
      "  N Cells:    16\n",
      "  N Points:   25\n",
      "  X Bounds:   0.000e+00, 4.000e+00\n",
      "  Y Bounds:   0.000e+00, 4.000e+00\n",
      "  Z Bounds:   0.000e+00, 0.000e+00\n",
      "  N Arrays:   1\n",
      "StressMeasuresAtNodes\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "ugrid = opsvis.get_unstruct_responses_dataset(\n",
    "    odb_tag=1, step=\"absMax\", ele_type=\"Plane\", resp_type=\"stressesAtNodes\", resp_dof=\"sigma_vm\", defo_scale=0.0\n",
    ")\n",
    "print(ugrid)\n",
    "print(ugrid.active_scalars_name)"
   ]
  },

   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {

   "source": [

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "7ae29b2d",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Thresholding"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 13,
   "id": "45c481c0",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/jpeg": "",
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=1024x768>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "threshed = ugrid.threshold([0.263, 0.573])\n",
    "\n",
    "p = pv.Plotter()\n",
    "p.add_mesh(\n",
    "    threshed, cmap=\"Spectral_r\", show_edges=True, show_scalar_bar=True, scalar_bar_args={\"title\": \"Von Mises Stress\"}\n",
    ")\n",
    "p.show(jupyter_backend=jupyter_backend, cpos=\"xy\")"
   ]
